<lb n="2" break="no"/>kum terivariya māṇikka
<lb n="3" break="no"/>malaimēl mannukiṉṟa
<lb n="4"/>tirukkōyil varuka ceka
<lb n="5"/>mutalāka nālakattuñ ce
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṅkilāya Aḷampā<unclear>ta</unclear>ta
<lb n="7" break="no"/>virntu naṭuvelā
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>ta</unclear> nittiruntapaṭi kaṇ
