<lb n="10" break="no"/>virataṅkoṇṭaruḷit tika
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḻa tirukkaṭṭaḷi cāttac cakameṅ
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ku nikaḻntōṉ Ālaivayalp 
<lb n="13"/>poḻilic civaṉat tampirān tō
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ḻan Āṭaviṭaṅkap piccan Aṭai
